          <caption>
            <p>Graphic results for causal network analysis of the Metabolic Syndrome in Men dataset, a mixed type dataset consisting of a categorical variable, genotypes of one index SNP at the <italic>ADIPOQ</italic> GWAS locus, and several continuous variables, including expression levels of 21 genes and plasma adiponectin levels (disease trait). The arrows indicate direction of causality. <bold>(A)</bold> mDAG; <bold>(B)</bold> MMHC; <bold>(C)</bold> CPC-stable.</p>
          </caption>
          <graphic xlink:href="fgene-11-00008-g003"/>
        </fig>
